        <div class="vision-mission-item">
            <div>
                <p>Our Vision</p>
                <h3 class="vision-mission-title mb-3">To Build a Trusted Pharmaceutical Brand with Purpose</h3>
                <p>Our vision is to establish Alvio Pharma as a trusted pharmaceutical organization recognized for both
                    the
                    quality of its medicines and the values that shape its culture. We aim to contribute meaningfully to
                    healthcare by improving patient outcomes, supporting healthcare professionals, and operating with
                    integrity at every level of our organization. Guided by our purpose of Improving Lives, we strive
                    for
                    sustainable growth rooted in responsibility and care.</p>
            </div>
